B[sr]
Dia. 02 Not one Point
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White can make points with 1.
\par How many points can he make?
\par
\par Do you think it is one point? That would be a hasty answer.
\par
\par Then 2 points? That is correct.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
